{
  "stem": "26140.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I still was very healthy and managed to survive whatever punishment I received.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, sometimes, if you-- if you stood for a while in-- to hide yourself from rain, if somebody see you, you-- you receive beating.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or if you tried to rest for a bit, you had to also watch that kapo doesn't come along to give you a beating for it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These are the things which usually worried me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The cruelty was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've seen-- I've seen the people in the penalty company being beaten.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had hard work doing-- and less food than we had.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was the worst part for me, when seeing people being thrown down the floor, pulled out gold teeth, and so on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "These were something I had never seen in my life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I feel a bit awkward.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's different than writing.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
